# .aignore — Paths excluded from AI file indexes, backups, and Drive sync.
# Parsed by watcher.py, backup.py, and drive.py on startup.
# Format: one path per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Prefix with workspace/ to target a specific subpath, or just a folder name
# to exclude it anywhere it appears in the tree.

# ── MODEL WEIGHTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CRITICAL: Never index, read, or sync model weight files.
# The GGUF alone is 18GB — reading it will exhaust any AI's context window
# and blow out Google Drive storage. These files are loaded directly by
# ExLlamaV2 and HuggingFace at runtime; no AI tool needs to see them.
models

# ── LARGE BINARY / GENERATED DIRS ─────────────────────────────────────────────
screenshots
backups
__pycache__
